{"about_the_game":"<strong>BEAUTIFUL DESOLATION</strong> is an isometric adventure set in a distant future. <strong>Explore</strong> a post-apocalyptic landscape, <strong>solve puzzles</strong>, <strong>meet</strong> new friends and make powerful enemies, <strong>mediate</strong> conflicts, and <strong>fight</strong> for your life as you unravel the secrets of the world around you. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/ratings.png?t=1721030556\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/epic.png?t=1721030556\" /><br><br>Mark, a man out of time, searches for his lost brother Don in a far-flung futuristic era ruled by highly advanced technologies, which are both revered and reviled. Your surroundings hold echoes of a desolate past and glimpses of a dark future that has yet to be written by your actions. Be prepared to face many tough choices that will shape this land long after you complete your journey. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/des_Boom.gif?t=1721030556\" /><br><br>The inhabitants of this world will help and hinder you as you make new discoveries and navigate the spectacular African-inspired landscape. Negotiate your passage with local leaders, healers, and warriors, or find yourself embroiled in a battle against nanite swarms, enormous scorpions, and rocket-equipped robots. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/des_Warden.gif?t=1721030556\" /><br><br>From thriving villages to crumbling cities, petrified forests, and bone-dry ocean beds, this strange new world holds a multitude of terrains to uncover.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/des_Fley.gif?t=1721030556\" /><